512 bytes (512 B) copied, 0.00540223 s, 94.8 kB/s
error: get_param: /proc/{fs,sys}/{lnet,lustre}/ldlm/services/ldlm_canceld/stats: Found no match
error: get_param: /proc/{fs,sys}/{lnet,lustre}/ldlm/services/ldlm_canceld/stats: Found no match
